node.text:
Live view of me preparing to carry you all away to Fall! 🛶🍂🍁
When should I start?!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kiel James Patrick on July 13, 2021 tagging @wonderful_places, @ilovegolden_retrievers, @beautifuldestinations, @earthpix, @earthroamer, @countrylivingmag, @goldenretrievers_, @bennieandmaple, @retrieverpuppies, @earth, @earthofficial, @earthfocus, @visualsofearth, @goldenretrieversworld, @travellingthroughtheworld, @earthoutdoors, and @goldenretrievers. May be an image of dog, lake and nature.

node.text: Bennie took Maple out for her first boat ride today.  They saw a turtle, barked at a duck and were the happiest I’ve ever seen them together 🥰😍🐢🦆🐕
